Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:26.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,活人滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:01.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他那副样子...
Comment: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:54.01,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/--------START---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:55.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西 这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用僧侣的皮骨打造出来的神像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是...是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亦不曾有过名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,无人知晓 埋于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:23.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道自己是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:26.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亦无人告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界没有我的立足之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不为人所需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亦不为人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚我出去捡垃圾为生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:47.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,白天则躲在洞穴中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:51.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,经过漫长岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的住所不知不觉间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成了地上人类的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我被埋在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被尸提压在坟墓底下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,无人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可就在我即将失去意识之时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇到了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,五位天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...天使?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:27.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使向我展示了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我得以知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世界充满了绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:37.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而我正在其最底层籍籍无名地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不禁呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以一种不知道是临死哀嚎还是初生之啼的呼声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使回应了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说愿意实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:05.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是孵化出「完美的世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我就是蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,「完美的世界」之蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望便是这个世界的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:21.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我注定为孕育新世界而生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界太不完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡毫不讲理地降临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:32.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些挣扎求存者的痛苦和恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:36.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以及为了掩盖那种浑沌而建立的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...充满了欺诈的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些安于扭曲的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在死亡面前互相推诿的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:49.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世界太丑陋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是想向这座城市的人复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,并非复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救那些丑陋卑鄙喜欢耍小聪明的懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救那些憎恨贪生怕死但还是要挣扎求存者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真正追求的只有一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是这个世界最不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既是最初亦是最后的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亦即是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,打...打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那些怪物有来有回 还稍占上风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:48.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然 他可是我看中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:50.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你跟着我积累修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会得到衣钵的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个黑色剑士一旦出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:05.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,便开始崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我所认识的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,轰隆 轰隆地 逐渐崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:19.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:25.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 烧掉信仰这层遮羞布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是个害怕黑夜的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:35.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放手 让我上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要死的是你!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么 什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我把他作为男人的那啥踢爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:58.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请您去完成自己神圣的任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:04.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我是有点乱了方寸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:08.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,保护师傅的任务就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:13.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,休想!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:16.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛铁拳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精凶杀脑天刺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:21.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:50.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所有一切已经向着那一刻发展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:54.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,包括你将那个魔女带到此地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也是征兆之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那个黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他也与之有关?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:08.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个是为了让「那位」降临这个世界所准备的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:13.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁? 如此渴求得到他们的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,「那位」很快便会现身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:29.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,当更多一直被当成蝼蚁般践踏的亡魂追寻「那位」之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界极其渺小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:33.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:38.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是用不曾在这个世界存在过的我作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:42.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,孵化出新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:43.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何带我来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何告诉我那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想在消失之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说说心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到他还有这等力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:12.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死神先生 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你们到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟尘世之人无关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你好 还是不要深究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 根据即将要发生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:29.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你对世间的认知或许会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:36.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 要道谢还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 若你继续顽抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仅剩的左眼也要失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:28.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等...且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:40.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来将以企图杀害僧侣的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,判处你车轮碾刑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:01.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,避不开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,避不开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大炮?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:22.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人的义肢里居然装了这么危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:29.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:31.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:50.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们因长相怪异而背负上的残酷命运最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您还为我们准备了这样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们遇到了摩兹古斯大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...这个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 又是这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 团长 你什么时候跑来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,地...地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟塔里面的怪物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是此地怨念形成的集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:10.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它们在呼应塔里面的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:14.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说打上烙印者共聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:18.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到门没开就能化成如此逼真的形体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,门?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,时机已到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:49.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们抓到了几十名企图从地牢逃走的邪教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:54.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都惊恐不已地说遇到了怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但都问不出来龙去脉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:59.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 法尔纳塞大人的下落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,报告 尚未发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:06.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾桑大人 这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若法尔纳塞大人有个三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想逃离烦人的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:21.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到边境之地安度晚年而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,发生何事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:51.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全军撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这座塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的很要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:27.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:37.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 佩佩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你去了也没什么用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:03.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:06.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:08.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,风?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是从难民窟传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:13.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...悲鸣?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:15.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 爸爸他...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:22.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是邪教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:36.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃去阿尔比安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:49.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全体尽量远离塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,空手的人帮忙搀扶伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副团长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请大发慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:44.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副团长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神明 庇佑!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩兹古斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天使 是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神仆们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,无需害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:09.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便邪魔的伎俩再怎么超乎寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要尔等信仰坚定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神一定会粉碎魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,展示神迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请看!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这副翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是神力的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:28.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是驱邪破魔之翼!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:41.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始对这个令邪恶蔓延圣地的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:44.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女执行火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:48.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为这不祥的异象打上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:49.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:04.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 趁吾等挡住魔物之际
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,速速竖起火柱!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副团长 我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士该做的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全军突击!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,保护民众!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个无情秃驴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,居然像扔石头一样扔人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 不知道格斯他们有没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,四位天使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,凭人的力量无法更改这个祭典的情节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会出现倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是由失去光芒的太阳所笼罩之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:37.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,投射至遥远人世间的倒影罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,倒影?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:43.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来都这么接近他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,烙印却没有剧痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一心不可二用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:07.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时候 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:12.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,烧死她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,烧死她 我们就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:22.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.60,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那么想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.94,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,没眼看
